{"article_id":"Xl66wSDIlVO11Npp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A growing number of Republican senators are calling for a delay on Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh 's confirmation vote","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"until they have time","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"to hear from a woman","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"accusing the judge of sexual misconduct","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"when they were both in high school .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford , 51 , came forward publicly Sunday with a detailed account in The Washington Post of an incident","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that took place at a party","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"when she was 15","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"and Kavanaugh was 17 .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Ford claims","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Kavanaugh held her down","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"and tried to remove her clothes","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"while covering her mouth with his hand","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"and leading her to believe","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"that he could `` inadvertently kill me . '' does not normally name accusers of sexual assault ,","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"but in this case , Ford forward publicly","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"to detail her allegations .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"The story of the alleged assault first appeared in a New Yorker magazine article last week ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"but Ford was not identified .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Since the story surfaced ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Kavanaugh has denied the allegations .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"In light of the allegations , a number of senators have said","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"they did n't want to move forward with advancing Kavanaugh 's nomination","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"until they heard from Ford .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Judiciary Committee Chairman Sen. Chuck Grassley , R-Iowa , said in a statement Monday","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"that anyone","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"`` who comes forward as Dr. Ford has","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"deserves to be heard . ''","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Still , his statement did not address","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"whether the committee would go forward with the nomination on Thursday","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"as planned .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Grassley said","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"the `` standard procedure ''","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"for handling late updates to `` any nominee 's background investigation file","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"is to conduct separate follow-up calls with relevant parties ''","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"Grassley he was trying to arrange calls with Kavanaugh and Ford .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"But he said","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"Sen. Dianne Feinstein , D-Calif. , refused to help him set the calls up .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"`` Unfortunately , committee Republicans have only known this person 's identity from news reports for less than 24 hours","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"and known about her allegations for less than a week , ''","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"Grassley said .","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"`` Senator Feinstein , on the other hand , has had this information for many weeks","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"and deprived her colleagues of the information","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"necessary to do our jobs . ''","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"He added","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that it was `` deeply disturbing '' that the allegations were `` leaked in a way","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"that seemed to preclude Dr. Ford ' s confidentiality ''","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"and lamented","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that Ford and Katz did not directly approach him with the allegations earlier .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"During an interview with NBC 's `` Today '' show , Ford 's lawyer , Debra Katz , said","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"her client was willing to testify .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"For his part , Kavanaugh released a statement Monday","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"that he would be willing to talk to the committee `` in any way","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"the Committee deems appropriate","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"to refute this false allegation , from 36 years ago ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and defend my integrity . ''","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Sen. Jeff Flake , R-Ariz. , one of the committee members , said","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"he does not think","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"the committee should advance Kavanaugh 's nomination","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"until Ford is heard out .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"`` If they push forward","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"without any attempt","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"with hearing what she 's had to say ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"I 'm not comfortable voting yes , ''","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Flake told Politico on Sunday .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"`` We need to hear from her .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"And I do n't think","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"I 'm alone in this . ''","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Sen. Bob Corker , R-Tenn. ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"who , like Flake , is retiring ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"told Politico","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"that it `` would be best for all involved ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"including the nominee ''","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"if the committee delayed a vote .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"`` If she does want to be heard ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"she should do so promptly . ''","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"When asked","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"if she believed","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"if the vote should be delayed ,","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"Sen. Lisa Murkowski , R-Alaska , told CNN on Sunday ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"`` I think","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"that might be something","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"they might have to consider . ''","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"`` This is not something","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"that came up during the hearings , ''","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"she said ,","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"according to CNN .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"`` The hearings are now over ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"if there is real substance to this ,","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"it demands a response . ''","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Although Murkowski and Corker are not on the Judiciary Committee ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Republicans only have a narrow , 51-seat majority in the Senate","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"and every vote will be crucial to Kavanaugh 's final confirmation .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"The Senate could bypass the committee","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"and bring Kavanaugh 's nomination directly to the floor for a vote .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Sen. Susan Collins , a moderate Maine Republican","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"whom groups opposed to Kavanaugh","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"have desperately tried to sway ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"said in a tweet Monday","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"that both Ford and Kavanaugh `` should both testify under oath before the Judiciary Committee. ``","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"On Monday , Collins told CNN","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"she was `` very surprised '' by the allegation against Kavanaugh .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"She said","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"she spoke to Kavanaugh about the allegations in a phone call Friday","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"and that the judge was `` very emphatic in his denial . ''","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"When asked if the vote should be delayed ,","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"she said","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"she would be talking to her colleagues ,","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"when asked","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"if she believed the accuser ,","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"she said","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"she did not `` know enough","depth":16},{"id":116,"text":"to make a judgment at this point . ''","depth":16},{"id":117,"text":"Collins told The New York Times on Sunday","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"that she found it `` puzzling ''","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"that Democrats did not come forward with the allegations earlier ,","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"`` after having had this information for more than six weeks . ''","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"`` If they believed Professor Ford ,","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"why didn ' t they surface this information earlier","depth":15},{"id":123,"text":"so that he could be questioned about it ? ''","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"Collins asked .","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"`` And","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"if they didn ' t believe her","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"and chose to withhold the information ,","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"why did they decide at the 11th hour to release it ?","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"It is really not fair to either of them the way","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"it is was handled . ''","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"Feinstein , a Judiciary Committee member , announced Thursday","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"she had forwarded a letter","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"containing the allegations","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"to the FBI , a day before the article in The New Yorker .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"Many Democrats were calling for a delay on Kavanaugh 's confirmation","depth":5},{"id":136,"text":"before the allegation surfaced ,","depth":5},{"id":137,"text":"but they have ramped up those demands in light of the accusation .","depth":4},{"id":138,"text":"`` For too long ,","depth":6},{"id":139,"text":"when women have made serious allegations of abuse ,","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"they have been ignored , ''","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. , said in a tweet on Sunday .","depth":5},{"id":142,"text":"`` That can not happen in this case . ''","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":285,"left":0,"right":284,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":284,"left":276,"right":283,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":163,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":147,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":1,"right":146,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":2,"right":145,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":3,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":160,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":158,"right":159,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":150,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":6,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":7,"right":148,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":155,"right":156,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":10,"right":154,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":151,"right":153,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":151,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":13,"right":152,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":275,"left":198,"right":274,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":198,"left":192,"right":197,"r